OL,3,CParents raise concern as island school
OL,4,Cclasses become 'too full'
OL,6,FThe average size of Maths and English
OL,7,Fclasses in Guernsey secondary schools
OL,8,Fhas risen by around 1.5 students over
OL,9,Fthe past two years, according to
OL,10,Fgovernment figures.
OL,12,FMaths and English classes have
OL,13,Fincreased in size across States of
OL,14,FGuernsey schools, with the largest
OL,15,Fbeing 34 students in a Maths class at
OL,16,FLes Beaucamps.
