OL,3,CParents raise concern as island school
OL,4,Cclasses become 'too full'
OL,6,FIt also follows that GCSE Maths grades
OL,7,Fin the island have worsened in
OL,8,Fstatistics, with parents raising
OL,9,Fconcerns that the two issues might be
OL,10,Flinked and impact their children's
OL,11,Feducation.
OL,13,FHowever, Guernsey's education
OL,14,Fdepartment has dismissed these claims,
OL,15,Farguing there is no evidence to
OL,16,Fsupport a correlation.
